001package org.opt4j.optimizers.ea;
002
003import org.opt4j.core.config.annotations.Name;
004
005/**
006 * Binds the {@link CouplerRandom} as the {@link Coupler}.
007 * 
008 * @author Fedor Smirnov
009 *
010 */
011@Name("Random")
012public class CouplerRandomModule extends CouplerModule {
013
014        @Override
015        protected void config() {
016                bindCoupler(CouplerRandom.class);
017        }
018}
